---
---

<section
  id="services"
  class="py-20 md:py-28 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto border-b border-primary-gold/55"
>
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="max-w-3xl mb-14 md:mb-16">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
      <span
        class="font-mono-tag text-[10px] text-primary-gold tracking-[0.4em] uppercase"
        >01 / EXPERTISE</span
      >
      <span class="flex-1 h-px bg-primary-gold/20"></span>
    </div>
    <h2
      class="text-2xl md:text-[38px] font-bold tracking-tight leading-[1.15]"
    >
      Soluciones técnicas con<br />
      <span class="font-serif-italic text-primary-gold text-[1.15em] font-normal"
        >sentido estético</span
      >
    </h2>
    <p class="font-mono-tag text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mt-5">
      Combinando ingeniería de software avanzada con un ojo clínico para el
      diseño minimalista de primer nivel.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Services Grid -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-primary-gold/15">
    <!-- Service 1 -->
    <div
      class="service-card group p-8 md:p-10 bg-[#0e0e0e] relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-[#131313]"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-gold/[0.03] to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"
      ></div>
      <div class="relative z-10">
        <span
          class="font-mono-tag text-[10px] text-primary-gold/50 group-hover:text-primary-gold transition-colors duration-300"
          >01</span
        >
        <h3
          class="text-xl font-bold mt-3 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary-gold transition-colors duration-300"
        >
          UI/UX Design
        </h3>
        <p class="font-mono-tag text-[13px] text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          Interfaces pensadas para la conversión de alta gama, utilizando
          principios estéticos de diseño editorial y minimalismo puro.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 2 -->
    <div
      class="service-card group p-8 md:p-10 bg-[#0e0e0e] relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-[#131313]"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-gold/[0.03] to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"
      ></div>
      <div class="relative z-10">
        <span
          class="font-mono-tag text-[10px] text-primary-gold/50 group-hover:text-primary-gold transition-colors duration-300"
          >02</span
        >
        <h3
          class="text-xl font-bold mt-3 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary-gold transition-colors duration-300"
        >
          Web Performance
        </h3>
        <p class="font-mono-tag text-[13px] text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          Desarrollo con Astro y arquitecturas SSG estáticas para lograr
          tiempos de carga instantáneos, SEO impecable y 100/100 en Lighthouse.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 3 -->
    <div
      class="service-card group p-8 md:p-10 bg-[#0e0e0e] relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-[#131313]"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-gold/[0.03] to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"
      ></div>
      <div class="relative z-10">
        <span
          class="font-mono-tag text-[10px] text-primary-gold/50 group-hover:text-primary-gold transition-colors duration-300"
          >03</span
        >
        <h3
          class="text-xl font-bold mt-3 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary-gold transition-colors duration-300"
        >
          Fullstack Logic
        </h3>
        <p class="font-mono-tag text-[13px] text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          Integración de bases de datos serverless rápidas, sistemas de
          autenticación y lógica transaccional robusta para aplicaciones
          fluidas a 60fps.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
